Rapid expansion of private hospital networks in China, India, and Southeast Asia, combined with rising healthcare expenditure, presents a sizeable untapped customer base for both fully and semi‑automatic devices. The region’s growing breast and liver cancer incidence creates a high demand for reliable core biopsy tools.
