Artificial intelligence algorithms capable of mapping optimal sampling zones can be embedded within spring‑loaded platforms. This integration promises higher diagnostic yield, reduced repeat procedures, and data‑driven workflow optimization, particularly valuable in high‑volume radiology suites.
Shift Toward Outpatient Care
The global trend toward same‑day, ambulatory procedures amplifies the need for rapid, safe, and patient‑friendly biopsy solutions. Spring‑loaded devices are ideally positioned to meet this demand, unlocking new revenue streams for manufacturers, distributors, and clinical providers.
